step_data.thought:
I can see that I'm now on the Products page in the Magento Admin interface. Looking at the page content, I can see there's a product listing table showing one product (Yoga Mat Pro). However, there appears to be a search filter applied, as indicated by the 'Active filters: Keyword: Yoga Mat Pro' section. To view all products in the inventory, I need to clear this filter.

I can see a 'Clear all' button with element ID [902] that will remove all active filters. Clicking this button should show all products in the inventory instead of just the filtered result.
